    <img id="Eq. F-13" class="img-thumbnail" src="~/Content/Images/Part75AppF.15.jpg" alt="Part 75 Appendix F Eq. F-13" title="Part 75 Appendix F Eq. F-13" />
    <br />
    <table>
        <tr>
